的定理，不难想到，我们只要找出某个整数 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"0 \\leqslant t < C"},{"type":"text","value":" 满足 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"G_t=G_{t+1}"},{"type":"text","value":"，则上述方程可转化为"}]},{"type":"math","value":"A^x = G_t \\times \\frac{A^t}{G_t} \\times A^{x-t} = G_t\\times D\\times A^{x-t}\\\\C=G_t\\times \\frac{C}{G_t}=G_t\\times C'\n"},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"不难发现，"},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"D"},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"C'"},{"type":"text","value":" 是互质的；因为 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"G_t=G_{t+1}"},{"type":"text","value":"，所以 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"A"},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"C'"},{"type":"text","value":" 也是互质的\n"},{"type":"footnoteReference","label":"3","identifier":"footnote-3"},{"type":"text","value":" 。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"接下来讨论 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"B"},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"G_t"},{"type":"text","value":" 的关系："}]},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"marker":42,"spread":true,"children":[{"type":"listItem","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"若 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"G_t \\mid B"},{"type":"text","value":"，结合前面给出的定理，有"}]},{"type":"math","value":"A^x \\equiv B \\mod C \\quad\\Rightarrow\\quad D\\cdot A^{x-t} \\equiv \\frac{B}{G_t} \\mod C'\n"},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"又因为 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"D"},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"C'"},{"type":"text","value":" 是互质的，所以存在模 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"C'"},{"type":"text","value":" 意义下的逆元 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"D^{-1}"},{"type":"text","value":"；进一步将同余方程化为"}]},{"type":"math","value":"\\displaystyle A^{x-t} \\equiv \\left(D^{-1}\\cdot \\frac{B}{G_t}\\right) \\mod C'\n"},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"由于 "},{"type":"inlineMath","value":"A"},{"type":"text","value":" 和 